e mine to keep. He has had a run in with God Magnus, who is his Brother, an=
d Valtron, the Maximal version of Galvatron. Valtron seems to think that Da=
rk Prime is the most evil thing in the universe, he seemed to forget about =
Unicron.

Why did you want to know all of this?
